'''James Kahn''' is the author of the [[Star Wars: Return of the Jedi (novelization)|''Star Wars Episode VI: Return of the Jedi'' novelization]]. This novelization was printed alongside its predecessors [[Star Wars: A New Hope (novelization)|''A New Hope'']] and [[Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back (novelization)|''The Empire Strikes Back'']] in the omnibus ''[[The Star Wars Trilogy]]''. The respective authors of the first two novels were [[Alan Dean Foster]] (credited as [[George Lucas]]) and [[Donald F. Glut]].

